text: Rajar Raja is a 1994 Indian Bengali film directed by Shamit Bhanja. The film stars Prosenjit, Debashree Roy, Abhishek Chatterjee and Rupa Ganguly in the lead roles. ==Cast== *Prosenjit *Debashree Roy *Abhishek Chatterjee *Roopa Ganguly *Haradhan Bandopadhyay *Koushik Bandyopadhyay *Debnath Chattopadhyay *Rahul Barman ==References== ==External links== * Category:1994 films Category:Indian films Category:1990s Bengali-language films
